description: Lists all fraudsters in a specified watchlist or domain.

nested_items.name: FraudsterSummaries
nested_items.description: A list that contains details about each fraudster in the Amazon Web Services account.

nested_items.name: CreatedAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when the fraudster summary was created.

nested_items.name: DomainId
nested_items.description: The identifier of the domain that contains the fraudster summary.

nested_items.name: GeneratedFraudsterId
nested_items.description: The service-generated identifier for the fraudster.

nested_items.name: WatchlistIds
nested_items.description: The identifier of the watchlists the fraudster is a part of.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If NextToken is returned, there are more results available. The value of NextToken is a unique pagination token for each page. Make the call again using the returned token to retrieve the next page. Keep all other arguments unchanged. Each pagination token expires after 24 hours.
